Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.20,0:00:49.25,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Touch and go, Catch the sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.39,0:00:55.75,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}为何我们相会于此？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.76,0:00:59.02,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}单纯的数字是无法证明的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.09,0:01:02.70,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}能让一切历史黯然无色的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:05.13,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}神秘大发现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:08.91,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}恰巧合适的 启示的密码
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.94,0:01:12.08,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}那是宇宙级的交感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.12,0:01:19.93,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}你能听见创造新纪元的胎动吗…？
