Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.57,0:01:26.29,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}创造出至高的未来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.37,0:01:33.20,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}乘上琥珀色的喷气飞机 向着争鸣的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.21,0:01:38.33,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}载满不成熟的梦想全力踩下油门
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.35,0:01:45.30,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}飞翔吧！一如所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.27,0:01:55.27,OPC1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Touch and go, Catch the sun!
