Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.52,0:22:21.45,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}立ち止まらず 歩いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.56,0:22:24.66,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}星を数えるように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.58,0:22:29.89,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}消せない絆が 光るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.18,0:22:37.33,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}夢は走り出した 僕らを導いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.54,0:22:41.70,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}願いを込めて　描く世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.82,0:22:46.92,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}守りたい 気持ちはきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.04,0:22:52.31,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}立ち向かう 勇気くれるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.52,0:22:55.54,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}まっすぐ伝えたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.72,0:22:58.57,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}歌うよ　La La La
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.79,0:23:01.77,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}届けて　La La La
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.97,0:23:05.98,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}忘れない 胸の奥で 輝いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.99,0:23:08.41,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}君がくれた光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.47,0:23:11.42,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}一緒に　La La La
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.45,0:23:14.39,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}願うよ　La La La
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.61,0:23:18.42,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}強く握りしめる手は 温かく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.57,0:23:23.87,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}このままずっと 離さないよ
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=================EDC=================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.52,0:22:21.45,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}一意向前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.56,0:22:24.66,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}就像在数着天上的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.58,0:22:29.89,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}永不消失的羁绊正在绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.18,0:22:37.33,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}梦想已然起步 它指引着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.54,0:22:41.70,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}倾注着梦想 描绘出这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.82,0:22:46.92,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}这份想要守护什么的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.04,0:22:52.31,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}定然会给我面对一切的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.52,0:22:55.54,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}因为我想直白地传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.72,0:22:58.57,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}唱歌吧 啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.79,0:23:01.77,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}接受吧 啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.97,0:23:05.98,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}在心底发光发热 永不会被忘却的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.99,0:23:08.41,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}是你给我的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.47,0:23:11.42,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}一起来 啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.45,0:23:14.39,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}许愿吧 啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.61,0:23:18.42,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}紧握的手儿是如此温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.57,0:23:23.87,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我永远也不会松开
